microprocessor_definition.description: Scans over a set of frequencies and detects transmitting antennas

object.script:
frequencyMin=0 frequencyMax=1000 frequency=frequencyMin frequenciesPerTick=13 delayFromAntennaToScriptInTicks=7 frequencyData={} foundFrequencies={} foundFrequenciesHistory={} frequencyStep=1 displayType=0 wasPressed=false displayBtn={x=1,y=1,w=25,h=7} tmpFound={} function onTick() frequencyMin=input.getNumber(29) frequencyMax=input.getNumber(30) frequenciesPerTick=input.getNumber(28) pressed=input.getBool(31) if wasPressed and not pressed and (mouseX>=displayBtn.x and mouseX<=displayBtn.x+displayBtn.w and mouseY>=displayBtn.y and mouseY<=displayBtn.y+displayBtn.h)then displayType=displayType+1 if displayType>2 then displayType=0 end end mouseX=input.getNumber(31) mouseY=input.getNumber(32) wasPressed=pressed for i=1,frequenciesPerTick do output.setNumber(i,frequency+(i-1)*frequencyStep) key=frequency+(i-1)*frequencyStep-delayFromAntennaToScriptInTicks*frequencyStep*frequenciesPerTick if key<0 then key=frequencyMax-key end video=input.getNumber((i-1)*2+1) compAudio=input.getNumber((i-1)*2+2) if input.getBool(32)then if key==frequencyMin+5*frequencyStep then compAudio=0.1 video=0.5 end if key==frequencyMax-12*frequencyStep then video=0.8 end end if compAudio>0 or video>0 then foundFrequencies[tostring(key)]={compAudio=compAudio,video=video}tmpFound[tostring(key)]={compAudio=compAudio,video=video} else foundFrequencies[tostring(key)]=nil end frequencyData[tostring(key)]={compAudio=compAudio,video=video} end frequency=frequency+frequenciesPerTick*frequencyStep if frequency>frequencyMax then frequency=frequencyMin table.insert(foundFrequenciesHistory,1,tmpFound) if SH and#foundFrequenciesHistory>SH-30 then table.remove(foundFrequenciesHistory,#foundFrequenciesHistory) end tmpFound={} end end
function onDraw() S=screen SW=S.getWidth() SH=S.getHeight() if displayType==0 then S.setColor(100,100,100) S.drawText(1,10,"Live") S.setColor(0,0,127) S.drawText(28,10,"Vid") S.setColor(127,0,0) S.drawText(50,10,"Cmp/Aud") for i=frequencyMin,frequencyMax,frequencyStep do d=frequencyData[tostring(i)]if not(d==nil)then if d.compAudio>0 then S.setColor(255,0,0,127) he=math.max(1,(SH-30)*d.compAudio) S.drawRectF((SW-1)*i/(frequencyMax-frequencyMin),SH-he,1,he) end if d.video>0 then S.setColor(0,0,255,127) he=math.max(1,(SH-30)*d.video) S.drawRectF((SW-1)*i/(frequencyMax-frequencyMin),SH-he,1,he) end end end S.setColor(0,255,0,127) S.drawRectF(SW*frequency/(frequencyMax-frequencyMin),0,1,SH) elseif displayType==1 then S.setColor(100,100,100) S.drawText(1,10,"Freq") S.drawText(SW-35,10,"Cmp/Aud") S.drawText(SW-55,10,"Vid") counter=0 keys={} for k,v in pairs(foundFrequencies)do table.insert(keys,k) end table.sort(keys) for k,v in ipairs(keys)do S.setColor(150,150,150) S.drawText(1,counter*8+20,v) S.setColor(127,0,0) S.drawTextBox(SW-40,counter*8+20,35,5,math.floor(foundFrequencies[v].compAudio*100).."%",1,0) S.setColor(0,0,127) S.drawTextBox(SW-60,counter*8+20,20,5,math.floor(foundFrequencies[v].video*100).."%",1,0) counter=counter+1 end elseif displayType==2 then S.setColor(100,100,100) S.drawText(1,10,"Live") S.setColor(0,0,127) S.drawText(28,10,"Vid") S.setColor(127,0,0) S.drawText(50,10,"Cmp/Aud") for a,b in ipairs(foundFrequenciesHistory)do for c,e in pairs(b)do i=c d=b[tostring(i)] if not(d==nil)then y=SH-a if d.compAudio>0 then S.setColor(255,0,0,127) S.drawRectF((SW-1)*i/(frequencyMax-frequencyMin),y,1,1) end if d.video>0 then S.setColor(0,0,255,127) S.drawRectF((SW-1)*i/(frequencyMax-frequencyMin),y,1,1) end end end end end S.setColor(120,120,120) S.drawText(displayBtn.x+displayBtn.w+6,1,math.floor(frequencyMin).." - "..math.floor(frequencyMax)) S.drawRectF(displayBtn.x,displayBtn.y,displayBtn.w,displayBtn.h) S.setColor(0,0,0) S.drawTextBox(displayBtn.x,displayBtn.y,displayBtn.w,displayBtn.h,"Mode",0,0)
if math.abs(frequencyMin - frequencyMax) < 1 then S.setColor(0,0,0) S.drawClear() S.setColor(100,100,100) S.drawTextBox(0,0,SW,SH,"select min and max frequency to scan",0,0) end end

-- With special thanks to XLjedi for providing the gamma correction function "gFix"
timer=0
function onTick() InputMax = property.getNumber("Input Max") Input1 = input.getNumber(1)/InputMax Input2 = input.getNumber(2)/InputMax Splash = property.getBool("Splash Enable") Horizontal = property.getBool("Horizontal Mode") Taper = property.getBool("Taper Mode") TaperLabelled = property.getBool("Taper Mode Labelled?") TaperLabel = property.getText("Taper Mode Label") TaperValueOn = property.getBool("Show Taper Value") HorizontalValue = property.getBool("Horizontal Value") if InputMax < 10 then TaperValue = string.format("%0.0f", input.getNumber(1)*100) .." %" HorizontalValue1 = string.format("%0.0f", input.getNumber(1)*100) .." %" HorizontalValue2 = string.format("%0.0f", input.getNumber(2)*100) .." %" else TaperValue = string.format("%0.1f", input.getNumber(1)) HorizontalValue1 = string.format("%0.1f", input.getNumber(1)) HorizontalValue2 = string.format("%0.1f", input.getNumber(2)) end Green1 = {0,131,49} Green2 = {0,158,29} Green3 = {0,226,50} Yellow1 = {255,231,39} Orange1 = {255,165,2} Orange2 = {255,127,39} Red1 = {255,0,49}
Inputs = {Input1, Input2}
--This is the table for segment colours. If you want to change a segment colour, edit the corresponding table entry below. scC = {Green1, Green1, Green2, Green2, Green3, Green3, Yellow1, Yellow1, Orange1, Orange1, Orange2, Orange2, Red1 ,Red1}
segmenttb = {}
if MonitorOn and timer<255 then timer=timer+1 end end function gFix(r,g,b) r=r^2.2/255^2.2*r g=g^2.2/255^2.2*g b=b^2.2/255^2.2*b return r,g,b end
function Gauge(inputnum) inputX = Inputs[inputnum]
if Horizontal == false then offset = ((inputnum-1)*15)
Yoffset = 0 else
Yoffset = ((inputnum-1)*15)
offset = 0
end
if inputnum > 4 then Yoffset = 32 end
for i = 14,1,-1 do screen.setColor(10,10,10) if Horizontal == false then screen.drawRectF(2+offset,(30-i*2)+Yoffset,13,1) elseif Taper == false then screen.drawRectF((1+i*2)+offset,2+Yoffset,1,13) else screen.drawRectF((1+i*2)+offset,2+Yoffset,1,5+i) end
if Horizontal == false and inputX > 0.071428*i then screen.setColor(gFix(table.unpack(scC[i]))) screen.drawRectF(2+offset,(30-i*2)+Yoffset,13,1) elseif Taper == false and inputX > 0.071428*i then screen.setColor(gFix(table.unpack(scC[i]))) screen.drawRectF((1+i*2)+offset,2+Yoffset,1,13) elseif inputX > 0.071428*i then screen.setColor(gFix(table.unpack(scC[i]))) screen.drawRectF((1+i*2)+offset,2+Yoffset,1,5+i) end end end
function onDraw()
MonitorOn=true w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
Gauge(1) screen.setColor(255,255,255)
if Taper and TaperLabelled then screen.drawTextBox(2, 26, w-4, 5, TaperLabel) end if Taper and TaperValueOn then screen.drawTextBox(2, 20, 100, 5, TaperValue) end
if Taper == false then Gauge(2) end
if Horizontal == true and HorizontalValue == true and Taper == false then screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawRectF(3,2,w,7) screen.drawRectF(3,17,w,7) screen.setColor(255,255,255) screen.drawTextBox(3,3,w,5,HorizontalValue1) screen.drawTextBox(3,18,w,5,HorizontalValue2) end
if Splash and timer < 150 then screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawRectF(0,0,w,h) screen.setColor(255,255,255) screen.drawTextBox(1,8,w-2,h-8,"Script by Xebec") end
if Splash and timer > 149 and timer < 250 then
screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawRectF(0,0,w,h) screen.setColor(gFix(49,123,196)) screen.drawLine(2, 27, 30, 0) screen.drawLine(3, 27, 31, 0) screen.drawLine(4, 27, 32, 0) screen.drawLine(5, 27, 33, 0) screen.drawLine(6, 27, 34, 0) screen.drawLine(7, 4, 22, 31) screen.drawLine(8, 4, 23, 31) screen.drawLine(9, 4, 24, 31) screen.drawLine(10, 4, 25, 31) screen.drawLine(11, 4, 26, 31) screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawRectF(0,8.75,16,3) screen.drawRectF(0,27.25,32,4.75) screen.drawRectF(0,0,32,6.25) end end
